Package ca.cgjennings.apps.arkham.plugins.typescript

Interface TypeScriptServices

public interface TypeScriptServices
Interface that provides direct access to language services from Java. Interface that defines the services The primary interface to TypeScript language services. This class allows you to hand off service requests to be performed in the background. A callback that you provide will be called with the result once it is available.
